---+++01-11-2018

Speech Recognition systems: CMU Sphinx and DeepSpeech

   Adapting acoustic and language models for our domains:
   * Giving commands to Robot: Here the speech vocabulary is limited because number of natural sentence is short and limited as well.So we do not need a very large 
     dictionary. In our work, we want to see how training the language model with small set of data can increase the accuracy.
   * Conversational ASR: The ASR systems gives a bad WER when used to recognise speech data with technical jargons and named entities. In our work we will adapt the ASR 
     system by extending the default models with our custom models. Our main focus would be to see how the WER improves after extending/adapting the models.


