   * (A Survey of Available Corpora for Building Data-Driven Dialogue Systems) https://breakend.github.io/DialogDatasets/
   * http://www.openslr.org/resources.php
   * read this paper: http://people.ict.usc.edu/~leuski/publications/papers/2013-sigdial-which-asr.pdf
   * Check dataset: http://www.speech.kth.se/prod/publications/files/4048.pdf
   * read the paper: Encoding Word Confusion Networks with Recurrent Neural Networks for Dialog State Tracking (https://arxiv.org/pdf/1707.05853.pdf)
   * read the paper: CONTINUOUS ASR FOR FLEXIBLE INCREMENTAL DIALOGUE (http://mi.eng.cam.ac.uk/~sjy/papers/bghk13.pdf)
   * read the thesis: Data-driven Methods for Spoken Dialogue Systems (http://kth.diva-portal.org/smash/get/diva2:906334/ATTACHMENT01.pdf)


